{"tid":825202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大西北輕鐵接近完全恢復服務","createTime":"2018-09-17T12:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:44:35.000Z","uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b31b24ed8bffdd8e7b620d5d0a2da9ae9ce50cd","tid":825202,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"輕鐵路綫505綫、507綫、610綫、614綫、615綫614P綫、615P綫、天水圍循環綫705及706綫維持正常服務：<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n751綫改道，將不停坑尾村站至天逸站。<br />\n <br />\n特別路綫751P綫，將行走來往天水圍站及天逸站。<br />\n <br />\n761P綫暫時未能提供服務。<br />\n <br />\n港鐵已安排免費接駁巴士，行走來往705綫沿途各站接載受影響車站的乘客。<br />\n <br />\n乘客亦請考慮改搭其他交通工具。<br />\n港鐵職員正在處理事件。請耐心等候，多謝合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日返工唔好搵籍口啦"},{"pid":"597e40930ad2b2d2bca19dfbc7464ad0c06e4017","tid":825202,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc607f3563b9343097bd237639346aa85fcf8d3","tid":825202,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d32332bd71135b0a308d5ebd424f0993ea5c8f8","tid":825202,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"冇751<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}